title: 6 Chess Books - October 2016 (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 6 chess books in PDF format:

1. After Magnus - Who Can Dethrone the World Chess Champion by Anish Giri
2. Chess Detective - Kriegspiel Strategies, Endgames and Problems by David H. Li
3. Chess Highlights of the 20th Century - The Best Chess 1900-1999 in Historical Context by Graham Burgess
4. Encyclopedia of Chess Combinations (4th Ed)(2012) by Chess Informant
5. Secrets of Chess Intuition by Alexander Belyavsky, Adrian Mikhalchishin
6. The King's Indian Defense by William Hartston, Leonard Barden & Raymond Keene
